Nope, highest ATM still only 23, and I have 3 others at level 5 waiting to sopec and test the new changes when they hit.<P>Do I need to read through the spell lists and actually point out how many different spells are in each line, and which ones can and cannot be overlapped? If you can't see matter as the thinnest then you are simply blind. Even on many topics I agree with here, it does not matter if that is not the way the class was intended.<P>NEWSFLASH!<P>Charm and Confusion will never work on another player!<P>We will never have a spell other than Amnesia out to near bolt range!<P>According to all statistical data, a sorceror can solo well ahead of the average XP over time Curve as desired by Mythic!<P>We will never have an invisibility spell!<P>Now there will be 3 spell paths as always. Right now, 2 are quite useful, and one is almost useless. It will be fixed, and we will have to decide between them. Deal with it. Get over it. All other casters have had to face this from the onset (for the most part) and now we will follow suit. For so long one line was so useless it became a non-issue for most. it was ignored. this was NOT the intent.<P>So now there will be 3 possible lines, and more ways to spec. And speccing heavy in one line excludes you from soem of the hgiher spells of another line. Now all those big brained sorcerors out there will have to make a real choice. Up till this point there was no choice, you kept Mind high for a pet, and the rest went into Body.<P>How boring do you want the sorceror to be? You will not be able to do everything. You shouldn't expect to be able to do everything. Right now 95% of sorcerors play the exact same. Think about the overall good of the class itself, and the balance of it in the realm as a whole, and THEN make those same statements. If you can your not being honest. <P>I am not here to cater to the whims of players who want their class to be the best at everything, or maybe not even the best at one thing. So when everyone here starts posting soem logs to PROVE how horrible we are, then I will have ammunition to take it further. but as it stands for every item soemone here screams about, there are 5 sorcerors on a live server who prove it utterly and completely wrong.<P>We can't get things changed because it doesn't favor YOUR particular play style. We can up a sorcerors solo power because 4 people here can't solo their way out of a wet paper bag. We need actual problems in the spells themselves.<P>Amnesia not working is a problem.<P>Run Spell not helping our pets is a problem.<P>Feeling jealous because a healer has an instant cast mez is NOT a problem!<P>So lets all focus on first fixing problems, then see how it pans out. Then if we are legitamately hurting when all things are working as planned, we can move to see how to adjust it to make things better.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...
